View.Name: WorkerInProcessingForm
View.CheckCode:
DefineVariables DEFINE ERHMS NETOBJECT "ERHMS Info Manager.Integration" DEFINE WorkerId TEXTINPUT End-DefineVariables
Field WorkerInfo_GetGlobalRecordId Click ASSIGN WorkerId = ERHMS.GetWorkerId(WorkerInfo_FirstName, WorkerInfo_LastName, WorkerInfo_EmailAddress, WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId) IF WorkerId <> "" THEN ASSIGN WorkerInfo_GlobalRecordId = WorkerId END-IF End-Click End-Field
